title: Brian Deegan on Lucas Oil Off Road Series qualifying at MMP
description: Brian Deegan brings the Metal Mulish Ford Ranger and F-150 Raptor to Miller Motorsports Park in Tooele, UT for the seventh and eighth rounds of the 2011 Lucas Oil Off Road Series. Deegan is currently second in both the Pro 2 Unlimited and the Pro  Lite Unlimeted championships heading into the weekend.
